{"tid":2359012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球促放人 美研新制裁  蓬佩奧：不容任意拘留美公民","createTime":"2021-01-08T14:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T14:15:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9470faaf781da1d1df6cfd62116014cfd051a1","tid":2359012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/QHLWI3MX3BF63CPVHN2KIWOR7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FQHLWI3MX3BF63CPVHN2KIWOR7U%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=9213e040\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FQHLWI3MX3BF63CPVHN2KIWOR7U%2F&h=dd5a58ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/QHLWI3MX3BF63CPVHN2KIWOR7U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全球促放人 美研新制裁 <br />\n蓬佩奧：不容任意拘留美公民<br />\n<br />\n【歹毒大搜捕】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政權以港版國安法大搜捕民主派初選人，繼英國及歐盟等國譴責後，美國國務卿蓬佩奧亦對事件表示憤怒，又對有美國公民遭警方以國安法逮捕感震驚，表明會考慮對中港施加新制裁。丹麥、加拿大、德國外長亦斥政府侵犯自由；聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處及對華政策跨國議會聯盟（IPAC）也發聲明，呼籲國際社會要以行動回應中港政府侵害香港民主及一國兩制。中國外交部隨即反擊蓬佩奧，聲稱美國要面對沉重代價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JQjUN_Qea3CbeIddBNsRQ8qOZbA=/1702x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SR2CXYFMHJE7VAYLBBWDUYWT2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJQjUN_Qea3CbeIddBNsRQ8qOZbA%3D%2F1702x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSR2CXYFMHJE7VAYLBBWDUYWT2A.jpg&h=d411ffd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民主動力司庫、美籍人權律師關尚義前日被捕，蓬佩奧對此深表震驚。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧昨發聲明，指今次大搜捕反映中國共產黨鄙視自己的人民和法治，對事。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b9J-gwOzCIsn7lwws3IqFT0irWA=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/34YIBGUJAJHTRHVGQOXGWUBCCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb9J-gwOzCIsn7lwws3IqFT0irWA%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F34YIBGUJAJHTRHVGQOXGWUBCCM.jpg&h=29347b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國國務卿蓬佩奧對港府大搜捕民主派初選人感到憤怒，表明會考慮對中港施加新制裁。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丹加德外長轟港府侵自由<br />\n<br />\n除了美國，丹麥外交大臣科福德也批評大搜捕行動，指事件令一國兩制成為幻象，強調行使民主權力並非犯罪，要求即時釋放被捕人士，表明會在歐盟討論此事。加拿大外長商鵬飛同樣要求釋放被捕人士，加拿大影子外長莊文浩更呼籲「是時候以《馬格尼茨基法案》讓那些人負責了」。<br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯也就事件發聲明，指大搜捕民主派初選人士，證明他們一直。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處發言人思羅塞爾就大搜捕發聲明，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIPAC促國際採果斷行動<br />\n<br />\n對華政策跨國議會聯盟（IPAC）發表聲明，呼籲所有民主國家在聯合國即時行動，尋求集體、懲罰性的經濟行動，使中國重新考慮其所為，而IPAC要求國際社會信守對港承諾，以果斷行動令中國就違反國際法負上責任，「拘捕行動證明中國和香港政權並不顧忌國際譴責，繼續破壞香港的自治、自由和法治，亦是違反《中英聯合聲明》和聯合國國際條約」。國際職工會聯盟亦發聲明，譴責港府大搜捕侵犯基本人權，聲援被捕的職工盟主席吳敏兒。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩再度「戰狼式」回應，要求美國停止干涉中國內政，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6fqw0cKfpGArhDET9UoiB1GyqXM=/1465x655/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OOQCAS3F2RCI3NSYSNKEB3KDDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6fqw0cKfpGArhDET9UoiB1GyqXM%3D%2F1465x655%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOOQCAS3F2RCI3NSYSNKEB3KDDI.jpg&h=f9800645&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dbf4647cea228ad355a4fbf2baf31d986923cad","tid":2359012,"uid":210140,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都無得撈啦"},{"pid":"769c3f70cc8cb7222e1c8fa83277ba73a624c7e1","tid":2359012,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}